reviewText: If you like 3&4 of the series this is a very good deal!
I had these movies on VHS, and now I see them on combined on DVD, I really enjoy his movies, thanks Amazon, this is added to my collection also.
Enjoyed I & II immensely.  Had to have whole series.  While sequels usually not as good; I was not disappointed.
These movies are classics, they don't make thim like this anymore so for me this was a great buy. Mr. T is one of my favorite actors, and Rocky 3 is Mr. T at his best can't go wrong with this buy.
